---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: tpch_q5"
---
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |  Sort: revenue DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   Projection: tpch.tpch.nation.n_name, sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) AS revenue                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[tpch.tpch.nation.n_name]], aggr=[[sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |       Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.nation.n_regionkey = tpch.tpch.region.r_regionkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |         Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey = tpch.tpch.nation.n_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |           Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey = tpch.tpch.supplier.s_suppkey AND tpch.tpch.customer.c_nationkey = tpch.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |             Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey = tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |               Inner Join:  Filter: tpch.tpch.customer.c_custkey = tpch.tpch.orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                 TableScan: tpch.tpch.customer projection=[c_custkey, c_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                 Filter: tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= CAST(Utf8("1994-01-01") AS Date32) AND tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < CAST(Utf8("1995-01-01") AS Date32)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                   TableScan: tpch.tpch.orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |               TableScan: tpch.tpch.lineitem projection=[l_orderkey, l_suppkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |             TableScan: tpch.tpch.supplier projection=[s_suppkey, s_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |           TableScan: tpch.tpch.nation projection=[n_nationkey, n_name, n_regionkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |         TableScan: tpch.tpch.region projection=[r_regionkey], full_filters=[tpch.tpch.region.r_name = Utf8("ASIA")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=spice.ai compute_context=url=https://flight.spiceai.io,username=,org=spiceai,app=tpch sql=SELECT n_name, sum((lineitem.l_extendedprice * (1 - lineitem.l_discount))) AS revenue FROM tpch.tpch.customer JOIN tpch.tpch.orders ON ((customer.c_custkey = orders.o_custkey) AND ((orders.o_orderdate >= CAST('1994-01-01' AS DATE)) AND (orders.o_orderdate < CAST('1995-01-01' AS DATE)))) JOIN tpch.tpch.lineitem ON (lineitem.l_orderkey = orders.o_orderkey) JOIN tpch.tpch.supplier ON ((lineitem.l_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey) AND (customer.c_nationkey = supplier.s_nationkey)) JOIN tpch.tpch.nation ON (supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_nationkey) JOIN tpch.tpch.region ON ((nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey) AND (region.r_name = 'ASIA')) GROUP BY nation.n_name ORDER BY revenue DESC NULLS FIRST rewritten_sql=SELECT "n_name", sum(("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount"))) AS "revenue" FROM "spice"."tpch"."customer" JOIN "spice"."tpch"."orders" ON (("customer"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey") AND (("orders"."o_orderdate" >= CAST('1994-01-01' AS DATE)) AND ("orders"."o_orderdate" < CAST('1995-01-01' AS DATE)))) JOIN "spice"."tpch"."lineitem" ON ("lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey") JOIN "spice"."tpch"."supplier" ON (("lineitem"."l_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey") AND ("customer"."c_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey")) JOIN "spice"."tpch"."nation" ON ("supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey") JOIN "spice"."tpch"."region" ON (("nation"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey") AND ("region"."r_name" = 'ASIA')) GROUP BY "nation"."n_name" ORDER BY "revenue" DESC NULLS FIRST |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
